                        <interp inst="t18580222-337-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">of Unlawfully Wounding</hi>.—(<hi rend="italic">The officer stated, that he had had three months for assaulting his wife, and one month for assaulting the police</hi>.)—<hi rend="italic">
